    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Biography"><a href="#Biography" class="headerlink" title="Biography"></a>Biography</h1><p>Huxin Gao received his Bachelor degree in Mechanical Engineering from Wuhan University, China in 2018. Currently, he is pursuing his PhD degree in Biomedical Engineering, National University of Singapore (NUS).</p><p>His main areas of interest include biomedical robotics, reinforcement learning, autonomous control, tactile-based control.</p><h1 id="Education"><a href="#Education" class="headerlink" title="Education"></a>Education</h1><p>01/2019 – present<br><strong>Ph.D</strong> in Biomedical Engineering<br><strong>National University of Singapore</strong>, Singapore</p><p>09/2014 –  06/2018<br><strong>B.Eng</strong> in Mechanical Design Manufacturing and Automation  <img src="/img/WHU_logo.png" alt="WHU_logo"><br><strong>Wuhan University</strong>, China</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
